<subSubSection pageId="810" pageNumber="811" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="810" pageNumber="811">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="810" pageNumber="811">
The range of this species extends from Newfoundland (Lindroth 1955a: 130) to east-central Alaska (Lindroth 1969a: 1056), south to the Sierra Nevada in California (Dajoz 2007: 16), southeastern Arizona (Graham and Greenlee Counties, UASM), central New Mexico (Fall and Cockerell 1907: 160), south-central South Dakota (Kirk and Balsbaugh 1975: 38), central Illinois (Wolcott 1895: 309), and western North Carolina (Yancey County, USNM) along the Appalachians. The records from 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Nebraska”">&quot;Nebraska&quot;</normalizedToken>
and 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Texas”">&quot;Texas&quot;</normalizedToken>
(Bousquet and Larochelle 1993: 274) need confirmation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
